
Fear , friendship , love , siblingsAll these things are destroyed by three things which are Jealousy , selfishness and finally misunderstanding and we will see all that happen in this story it's all about how a very strong friendship can be destroyed because of selfishness and how a very powerful relationship between a brother and a sister could make them strangers because of a misunderstanding between them all these we will talk about and explain it in a story. I am sky and this is the story of my life.A N.H fan fiction